{"tid":258756,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州出席手錶品牌活動　被指「言行失當」　方中信遭終止代言人合約","createTime":"2017-05-26T11:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T12:03:16.000Z","uid":52651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eee686212a293060f02d7e9281b85db444dfeb1f","tid":258756,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E6%89%8B%E9%8C%86%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E8%A8%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6-%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%A1%E9%81%AD%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E4%BB%A3%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25B7%259E%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%258C%2586%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%2595%25B6-%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584%2F&d=X4fZAkDwfXTc2TgTMdGF6Gxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=cbcb1caa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25B7%259E%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%258C%2586%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%2595%25B6-%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584%2F&h=3a8615da\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E6%89%8B%E9%8C%86%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E8%A8%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6-%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%A1%E9%81%AD%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E4%BB%A3%E8%A8%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84/</a><br />\n<br />\n「瑞士時度表」DOXA亞太區總代理邁拿鐘表今於報章和Facebook刊登啟事指，因藝人方中信上周六（20日）出席品牌活動時言行失當，破壞了邁拿鐘表與DOXA的形象，故決定即時終止方中信作為品牌代言人身分。<br />\n<br />\n時度表亞太區總代理邁拿鐘表國際有限公司以及其於廣州、上海、北京公司今於報章和Facebook專頁刊登啟事，聲明「DOXA不再與藝人方中信合作」，內容指於本月20日，方中信出席品牌活動時言行失當，「完全與其品牌代言人的身分不符，以致公司管理層及在場嘉賓尷尬萬分」，「嚴重破壞」該公司及DOXＡ品牌經多年建立的形象和聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n邁拿鐘表指，「為維護本公司、DOXA品牌及各友好合作夥伴等商業利益，本公司決定即時終止方中信作為品牌代言人的身分」。<br />\n<br />\n東方日報報道指，據悉事件涉及客戶飯局和拍照之類的問題，而報道引述方中信所屬之英皇公司經理人霍汶希昨指，經理人公司在合約上會為演出藝人訂明工作範疇，但以外的事，藝人有權拒絕，她又指，合約是由對方單方面終止。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，方中信於本月20日在廣州，出席DOXA與珠寶店舉辦的旗艦店開業活動，邁拿鐘表國際有限公司的首席營運總監亦有出席。"},{"pid":"4042fa3c6b96095a2a7f1ae687516466d877527f","tid":258756,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"有冇文字描述點失當法？"},{"pid":"6144ad89045f413ec51d3114ab468439d2a6e8b5","tid":258756,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇文字描述點失當法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又真係無講.......奇奇怪怪"},{"pid":"2482837af3682f53b51e25454c30bd9e36a65b70","tid":258756,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170526/56745331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170526%2F56745331&d=X4fZAkDwfXTc2TgTMdGF6Gxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=9741fd30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170526%2F56745331&h=d05eb385\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170526/56745331</a>"},{"pid":"4715b3b4bd74bb63b3c8b3ac5c42561aec80235c","tid":258756,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:25:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇文字描述點失當法？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又真係無講.......奇奇怪怪</blockquote><br />\n照計要話一個代言人言行失當<br />\n通常都係要衰到 上報紙上新聞個類負面新聞姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s